data.description: LOCATION !!! LOCATION !!!  Big drop in Sales Price !!!  Single-story ranch-style home on the West side of town. Charming covered front porch with lovely landscaping and artificial grass. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home with a large office and a 2 car detached garage is perfect for any buyer. Open floor plan with a brick fireplace. Living room has wood Cathedral ceilings with wood beams. Kitchen features a large island and nice appliances. Two large bedroom with ceiling fans, one with cabinets and shelving. Office or den also with Built-in cabinets. Master bedroom is large with 2 closets and entrance out to the back yard patio. Back yard with fencing, large pergola providing plenty shade and entertainment area. Brick patio and utility shed. This lovely home is 7 miles from Mountain High Ski area and within walking distance to elementary school and town.
